     1	---
     2	title: Engine Subsystem Design
     3	date: 2026-05-12
     4	target_release: 0.6.0
     5	desc: Runtime open/close, writer/read path, engine config, cursor semantics, and canonical-row supersession
     6	blast_radius: fathomdb-engine runtime/writer/reader; interfaces/*.md; acceptance.md REQ-020..REQ-055 intersections
